@117    = ~Hourglass~
@118    = ~This small hourglass is made from exquisitely worked metal and filled with fine, pale sand. Its craftsmanship suggests that it may be more than an ordinary timepiece.~

@119    = ~Figurine~
@120    = ~This finely carved animal figurine depicts a large black panther. Its polished stone surface is cool to the touch.~

@121    = ~Ring~
@122    = ~This metal ring is plain except for a faintly shimmering band around its edge. Its purpose is not apparent.~

@123    = ~Robe~
@124    = ~This heavy mage robe is woven from dark, age-worn fabric. Traces of powerful magic cling to its folds.~

@125    = ~Long Sword~
@126    = ~The blade of this well-crafted long sword bears faint discoloration along its edge. Its unusual balance suggests that it is no ordinary weapon.~
